title: Hinterland - S01 E03 (Redone) - Sno
description:
Hinterland - S01 E03 (Redone) - Sno 

Redone as there were sync issues with original upload - Sorry ;(


This was originally aired in 7 parts. The First Episode was broadcast whole - whilst the 3 other episodes were split into 2 parts. I have combined the split episodes together to make them complete.Well shot and heavily influenced by Scandinavian Drama.

Welsh speaking parts have Hardcoded Eng Subs

3/4  In the isolated village of Penwyllt, the body of a young man is found in the murky depths of a quarry lake, and the investigation draws Mathias into the heart of the close-knit community.
Mathias is then drawn deeper into the complex web of the Penwyllt community as he questions what drove Gwilym to commit suicide. As he continues to investigate what lies behind the animosity between Bratton and the other villagers, he tries to discover what is the nature of the relationship between Lowri and Bratton.
